# Key Insights from Dashboard

* Diagnosis rate increases significantly with chronic pain level
* Obese patients have the highest diagnosis rate (~51%)
* Pain level is a stronger predictor than BMI
* Patients with both high BMI and high pain fall into the highest risk category

## Business/Clinical Value

This dashboard helps in:

* Early identification of high-risk patients
* Supporting clinical decision-making
* Understanding symptom-driven diagnosis patterns
